history.content:
It is highly unlikely any additional upper division courses will be offered that aren't already for summer 2018.  We've never been able to offer more than 3 upper divs in any given semester (for lack of interested/qualified instructors).

We would like to expand the size of the current listings but that depends on two things:

1) instructor willingness

2) enough qualified TAs to cover sections -- since potential upper div ugsi's might rather work an internship and gsis often need to focus on their research over the summer that is always hard.

As of now only CS 160, 188, and 189 are being offered this summer. Of these 3, only 189 has open seats. Are there plans to offer other CS upper div summer classes or expand the class sizes of the current listings?
history.subject: Upper Division Course Listings - Summer 2018
